.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-SET-FEE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-set-fee \- set routing fee policy for a channel
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-set-fee
.I channel_id
.B --base
.I msat
.B --ppm
.I ppm
.SH DESCRIPTION
Sets the base fee (in millisatoshis) and proportional fee rate
(parts-per-million) for an outbound channel via
.BR setchannel .
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"ok":true,"channel_id":"...","base_msat":N,"ppm":N}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-fee-policy (1),
.BR lightning-api-fee-list (1)
